OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FA family have been left thousands of
OL,7,Fpounds out of pocket after the
OL,8,Fcollapse of a major law firm, PM
OL,9,FProperty Law.
OL,11,FGabriella Smith, who lives in Barry
OL,12,Fwith her husband and young daughter,
OL,13,Fwas in the process of re-mortgaging
OL,14,Fher family home when the Sheffield-
OL,15,Fbased PM Property Law closed abruptly
OL,16,Fin February. She is now one of
OL,17,Fthousands across the UK affected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
