PN,46102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FThe Solicitors Regulation Authority
OL,7,F(SRA) has confirmed its ongoing
OL,8,Finvestigation involves a
OL,9,F"sophisticated suspected fraud" and
OL,10,Fthe "improper removal and misuse of
OL,11,Faround #39.5 million" of client funds,
OL,12,Fmaking it one of the largest and most
OL,13,Fcomplex cases the regulator has ever
OL,14,Fundertaken.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FEven though their new mortgage was
OL,7,Ffinalised in January 2026, the
OL,8,Fcritical redemption payment to clear
OL,9,Ftheir old mortgage was never made,
OL,10,Fdespite Gabriella having received
OL,11,Fconfirmation that the payment had been
OL,12,Fsent to the old provider.
OL,14,FWith the old account still active and
OL,15,Fthe new mortgage payment commencing,
OL,16,Fthe couple initially found themselves
OL,17,Fhaving to pay two mortgages causing
OL,18,Fimmediate, severe financial strain.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,F"Since that moment, the stress and
OL,7,Ffinancial strain have been
OL,8,Foverwhelming," Gabriella said.
OL,10,FAlthough the issue of paying two
OL,11,Fmortgages has been resolved in recent
OL,12,Fweeks, the initial dual payments added
OL,13,Fsignificant financial strain and was a
OL,14,Fmajor reason why the family needed a
OL,15,Fnew solicitor to take over the stalled
OL,16,Fconveyancing process.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,F"We kept being told we needed a
OL,7,Fsolicitor to act on our behalf to
OL,8,Fwhich I said to them how do we get a
OL,9,Fnew solicitor when we don't have the
OL,10,Fmoney to pay for a new solicitor,"
OL,11,FGabriella explained.
OL,13,F"As far as we were concerned we'd paid
OL,14,FPM Property Law to do the work of the
OL,15,Fsolicitor to remortgage so why were we
OL,16,Fin need to get a new one that would
OL,17,Fcost us and has cost us thousands."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FThe family has been forced to borrow
OL,7,Fmore than #4,000 from relatives to
OL,8,Fcover the costs of a new solicitor and
OL,9,Fassociated fees, money they simply do
OL,10,Fnot have.
OL,12,F"This isn't our mistake that we've
OL,13,Fmade, we haven't done anything wrong,"
OL,14,FGabriella said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,F"We've always kept up with our
OL,7,Fmortgage payments, we followed the
OL,8,Fprocedure we needed to follow to
OL,9,Fremortgage and as far as we were
OL,10,Fconcerned everything was in place and
OL,11,Feverything had gone through just fine
OL,12,Fso no I don't feel we should be out of
OL,13,Fpocket".
OL,15,FThe long-term impact and lack of
OL,16,Freimbursement has left Gabriella
OL,17,Ffeeling "very betrayed" and
OL,18,F"frightened" about future legal
OL,19,Ftransactions.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FThe collapse of PM Law Ltd has not
OL,7,Fonly financially impacted Gabriella
OL,8,Fand thousands of others, but it has
OL,9,Fraised huge questions about how a
OL,10,Ffailure of this magnitude was allowed
OL,11,Fto happen.
OL,13,FRichard Orpin, Chief Executive of the
OL,14,FLegal Services Board (LSB), the body
OL,15,Fthat oversees the SRA, admitted that
OL,16,Fthe regulatory system has failed
OL,17,Fconsumers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,F"It's really essential that when
OL,7,Fpeople use the services of a law firm
OL,8,For a solicitor, they can be confident
OL,9,Fthat their money is safe," Mr Orpin
OL,10,Fsaid. "We've seen that over recent
OL,11,Fyears, the SRA's approach hasn't been
OL,12,Fas effective as it should be".
OL,14,FDespite rules being in place, Mr Orpin
OL,15,Fstressed that the LSB is "requiring
OL,16,Fthe SRA to go much faster and much
OL,17,Ffurther to strengthen its rules and
OL,18,Fensure that people are protected".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FWhen asked about the situation facing
OL,7,Fclients like Gabriella Smith, who have
OL,8,Fincurred thousands in non-reimbursable
OL,9,Fcosts, Mr Orpin offered his "heartfelt
OL,10,Fsympathy".
OL,12,FHe clarified the limits of the SRA's
OL,13,Fcompensation fund: "The SRA does have
OL,14,Fa compensation fund now. It is a fund
OL,15,Fthat has some discretion over so while
OL,16,Findirect losses are not automatically
OL,17,Fcovered, it may be possible for them
OL,18,Fto be covered in certain
OL,19,Fcircumstances". He urged anyone
OL,20,Faffected to "get in touch with the SRA
OL,21,Fand explore what the options might be".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FThe PM Law group was made up of 11
OL,7,Fcompanies, 25 offices and more than 30
OL,8,Ftrading names. Its collapse led to
OL,9,Fimmediate chaos, with files frozen,
OL,10,Ftransactions delayed, and client money
OL,11,Ftemporarily inaccessible.
OL,13,FThe SRA acknowledged the severity of
OL,14,Fthe case and, while unable to comment
OL,15,Fon individual cases, confirmed they
OL,16,Fare actively supporting those affected.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,FPaul Hastings, SRA Director of Client
OL,7,FProtection, said: "We are continuing
OL,8,Fto do all we can to support former
OL,9,Fclients of PM Law, including by
OL,10,Freuniting them with their money or
OL,11,Ffiles."
OL,13,FHe added that those affected include
OL,14,Fclients "in the process of buying or
OL,15,Fselling a home, facing the risk of
OL,16,Fcollapsed moves, or losing their
OL,17,Fdeposits". Others were dealing with
OL,18,Fcomplex and stressful matters such as
OL,19,F"delayed probate matters, often while
OL,20,Fmanaging bereavement and outstanding
OL,21,Festate administration".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778746040
OL,3,CFamily lost thousands of pounds after
OL,4,Ccollapse of major law firm
OL,6,F"Many of the former clients faced
OL,7,Fsignificant upheaval at a stressful
OL,8,Ftime, so we have been determined to
OL,9,Fprovide as much support as possible,"
OL,10,FMr Hastings stated.
OL,12,FThe SRA has so far paid out millions
OL,13,Ffrom its compensation fund and seized
OL,14,Fclient money to resolve cases, but the
OL,15,Ftotal number of claims linked to the
OL,16,Fcollapse is estimated to be rising.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
